{"tid":1876944,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"WFH 真係好正","createTime":"2020-02-12T17:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T04:18:59.000Z","uid":11077,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8af458e4f50476b4d3c752666703f129a3053cd6","tid":1876944,"uid":11077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:33:42.000Z","msg":"每日起身開電腦再慢慢食早餐, 睇住街上面D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 開outlook check 下email, 每日SEND十封email差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂<br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街排口罩, 或者買廁紙 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就喺屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\nWFH左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來WFH已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"84b3bef0a25bbd126149a7aecf1a17f93b8d1218","tid":1876944,"uid":126372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:35:42.000Z","msg":"必要時返office交通都快好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00306d1034207defc2d9571c100df56b51987bbe","tid":1876944,"uid":119875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"可以考慮落街100蚊買2個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047b099c73995905f810d19c6dafa6ae5ce4aebb","tid":1876944,"uid":47222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"本來搭車既時間仲長過而家做野既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3195a4993f0ccfcac8fd0572a869d5ae634d0f6d","tid":1876944,"uid":293368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:41:34.000Z","msg":"唔係個個WFH都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178738d21064fbe64e10e695c7e9272855e5fcf3","tid":1876944,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:41:37.000Z","msg":"潮文嚟，見過裸辭搵工版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo